{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L982"},"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation’s callout view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The control that was tapped."}]}],"name":"control"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"text":" class, the map view calls this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, you can specify the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom accessory views using the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclass that displays information about a selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation near that annotation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNCalloutView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNCalloutView","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documenta